<br>
Idea:<br>
<br>
Just for an example let's say there are 6 guilds that were interested in this...these 6 guilds would have to have the potential of killing Sev on their own IE guilds that had no chance of killing him wouldn't be fair to let in on this.  These 6 guilds form a somewhat &quot;Sev Alliance.&quot;  These guilds then check on Sev often throughout the day and night.  If he is up then every guild in the &quot;alliance&quot; sends all the help they can right away to kill Sev.  From there a rotation could be setup from which guild gets the loot.  Then the next time he pops each guild does the same, and then the next guild gets the loot.  So on and so on.<br>
<br>
